   M /io_lib/trunk/io_lib/cram_encode.c

Fixed crash when encoding using more than 1 slice per container and
are using referenceless mode.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r3289 | jkbonfield | 2013-04-23 10:32:26 +0100 (Tue, 23 Apr 2013) | 6 lines
