   M /io_lib/trunk/io_lib/sam_header.c
   M /io_lib/trunk/io_lib/sam_header.h

Major speed increase to sam_header_find() when given SQ/SN, RG/ID or
PG/ID requests.  It uses the prebuilt hashes instead.


