------------------------------------------------------------------------
r3191 | jkbonfield | 2013-03-08 15:24:11 +0000 (Fri, 08 Mar 2013) | 9 lines
Changed paths:
   M /io_lib/trunk/io_lib/bam.h
   M /io_lib/trunk/io_lib/cram_decode.c
   M /io_lib/trunk/io_lib/cram_encode.c
   M /io_lib/trunk/io_lib/cram_index.c
